{"tid":23890,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"三文魚黎講挪威靚定日本靚","createTime":"2016-12-05T08:27:31.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-05T13:48:36.000Z","uid":26834,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"47df76396577c013a7708c9707bf8e1d9a842671","tid":23890,"uid":26834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T08:27:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4c942cc4b733ef9b3e95e24bd1cc38552fd4147","tid":23890,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T09:45:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f0bc76016ca6584f8aa541d91c604aef55269820","tid":23890,"uid":35070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T09:48:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20070520/large/20lp2p2zok.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20070520%2Flarge%2F20lp2p2zok.jpg&h=8d35cc61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我又要出動了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0f6d14dc1d16f3808b24fc193b76c0c6f07aeb3","tid":23890,"uid":35070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T09:49:17.000Z","msg":"最新一期《新英倫醫學雜誌》指，日本有人進食三文魚後，出現胸痛、作嘔等病徵，醫生透過內窺鏡，在她體內鉗出11條寄生蟲「異尖線蟲」幼蟲，非常嚇人。<br />\n<br />\n著名食家蔡瀾曾撰文指，日本人並不會出售三文魚刺身，因為他們知道三文魚刺身有很多蟲。我們致電蔡瀾，他直言：「直情不吃。我已經說過很多次，文中又有寫，微博又有寫，但無人理我，繼續食」、「大陸那些餐廳，一大碟三文魚刺身，這是很避忌的事，食完會生蟲」。<br />\n<br />\n2015年，網上曾流傳一張連鎖壽司店爭鮮（香港）的海報，宣傳以虹鱒製作的「鱒三文魚餐盒」，引起討論，因為虹鱒一般在淡水棲息，並不會當作刺身食用。我們致電爭鮮（香港）查詢，爭鮮（香港）指他們現時只出售挪威三文魚產品，並無使用虹鱒。至於其他連鎖店如元氣壽司、千両和帝皇飲食集團旗下的日式放題餐廳亦回覆稱，他們採用挪威養殖的三文魚，並有嚴格的安全指引及嚴密的安全監測，亦沒有採用淡水虹鱒魚。<br />\n<br />\n吃刺身時，好多人以為蘸Wasabi可以殺菌，不過寧波市疾控中心2006年發表的《東海魚類異尖線蟲感染調查及其幼蟲對青芥辣的耐受研究》就指，最少要把刺身浸在Wasabi55分鐘才有效。<br />\n<br />\n至於三文魚的保存方法，香港魚類學會會長莊棣華指，日本規定三文魚須在零下20度急凍最少廿四小時，確保殺死寄生蟲。但他亦提醒，一般市民沒有急凍至零下20度的設備，建議大家食用時，應跟從包裝上的指示，要煮熟的必須煮熟，這樣才會吃得安心。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/supplement/food/art/20160828/19751841\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fsupplement%2Ffood%2Fart%2F20160828%2F19751841&d=NiOc6rc%2FE9fikVhzT7%2F1G0sIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=bc549f5d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fsupplement%2Ffood%2Fart%2F20160828%2F19751841&h=b3f0431f\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/supplement/food/art/20160828/19751841</a>"},{"pid":"9b6c216add42ddb7a2a7f2ae374316844f805d2c","tid":23890,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T10:35:29.000Z","msg":"一定係挪威<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n日本水溫唔夠凍根本就冇咁高脂肪嘅三文魚出產，即使去到北海道果邊夠凍，都缺少天然環境比三文魚棲息<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有識食一定唔會生食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n試過king salmon煎到medium rare保證你返唔到轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44a01d770b12d27a3a9ab5134edd10cdec6e8388","tid":23890,"uid":7026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T13:48:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20070520/large/20lp2p2zok.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20070520%2Flarge%2F20lp2p2zok.jpg&h=8d35cc61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我又要出動了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}